title: Ebro In The Morning - The Day Facebook Died + Guest: Erica Ford
itunes:author: Ebro In The Morning on HOT 97
itunes:summary:
Ebro, Rosenberg and Laura Stylez star in HOT97's flagship program Ebro in the Morning - this episode aired on 10/5.

Ebro and the crew talk about the death of the internet. Laura Stylez has her patented Flashing Lights segments at minutes 7, 50:30, and 1:27.

Please like and subscribe to Ebro In The Morning.

(Minute 30) Erica Ford of Life Camp Inc. joined Ebro in the Morning to discuss how we as a people can help assist in helping shift the culture to bring more resources to help kids & teenagers and lower the amount of gun violence in NYC and across the nation. Join the Peace March at 10/11 starting at the Barclays Center at 11 AM EST. 

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
